			"command"	 "play buttons/button14;show_menu KickPlayer"
			"label"		 " Kick Player"
		}
		"2"
		{
			"command"	 "play buttons/button14;show_menu BanPlayer"
			"label"		 " Ban Player"
		}		
		"3"
		{
			"command"	 "play buttons/button14;sb_add;show_menu KickBanPlayer"
			"label"		 " Restore Bot"
		}
		"4"
		{
			"command"	 "play buttons/button14;kick nick;kick rochelle;kick coach; kick ellis;kick bill;kick zoey;kick louis;kick francis;show_menu KickBanPlayer"
			"label"		 " Kick Bots"
		}
	    "8"
		{
			"command"	 "play buttons/button14;show_menu Admin"
			"label"		 " << Back"
		}
		" "
		{
			"command"	 "play buttons/button14;show_menu Admin"
			"label"		 " "
		}
		"0"
		{
			"command"	 "play buttons/button14"
			"label"		 " Exit"
		}

	"ent_particles_settings"
	{
			"Title"		 "Settings"
			"1"
			{
					"command"    "play buttons/button14;show_menu ent_particles_duration_settings"
					"label"      " Update preferred attachment duration"
			}
			"2"
			{
					"command"    "play buttons/button14;scripted_user_func attach_to_targeted_position;show_menu ent_particles_settings"
					"label"      " Enable/Disable attaching to targeted location"
			}
			"3"
			{
					"command"    "play buttons/button14;scripted_user_func randomparticle_save_state;show_menu ent_particles_settings"
					"label"      " Enable/Disable saving last particle spawn"
			}
			"4"
			{		
					"command"    "play buttons/button14;scripted_user_func display_saved_particle;show_menu ent_particles_settings"
					"label"      " Display information of saved particle"
			}
			
			"8"
			{
					"command"    "play buttons/button14;show_menu ent_particles_main1"
					"label"      " << Back"
			}

			"0"
			{
					"command"    "play buttons/button14"
					"label"      " Exit"
			}
	}

                    "command"	 "play buttons/button14;scripted_user_func model_scale,!self,0.75;show_menu models_self_scale1"
                    "label"		 " Small ( 0.75 )" 
            }
			"5"
            {
                    "command"	 "play buttons/button14;scripted_user_func model_scale,!self,2.0;show_menu models_self_scale1"
                    "label"		 " Big ( 2.0 )" 
            }
			"6"
            {
                    "command"	 "play buttons/button14;scripted_user_func model_scale,!self,4.0;show_menu models_self_scale1"
                    "label"		 " Bigger ( 4.0 )" 
            }
			"7"
            {
                    "command"	 "play buttons/button14;scripted_user_func model_scale,!self,8.0;show_menu models_self_scale1"
                    "label"		 " Biggest ( 8.0 )" 
            }
			"8"
			{
					"command"    "play buttons/button14;show_menu models_menus"
					"label"      " << Back"
			}
			"0"
			{
					"command"    "play buttons/button14"
					"label"      " Exit"
			}
	}

    "models_picker_scale1"
	{
			"Title"     "Scale factors (Only works for a few models)"
			"1"
            {
                    "command"	 "play buttons/button14;scripted_user_func model_scale,!picker,1.0;show_menu models_picker_scale1"
                    "label"		 " Default Scale ( 1.0 )" 
            }

            {
